Title: Star Trek: Enterprise
Actors: Scott Bakula, John Billingsley, Jolene Blalock
Plot: A century before Captain Kirk's five-year mission, Jonathan Archer captains the United Earth ship Enterprise during the early years of Starfleet, leading up to the Earth-Romulan War and the formation of the Federation.
Awards: Won 4 Primetime Emmys. 14 wins & 50 nominations total
